desc: ROBOCUP is a patented portable clamp on caddy cup holder for drinks, keys, phone, tools, gear drum sticks and more. Perfect for a boat, fishing, RV, tractor, camping, wheelchair, walker, mobility scooter, film & photography stands, musicians, equipment carts and golf carts. Plus and Holster add-ons are available now.

layout.text: Patented Portable Caddy with a World of Uses
